My day at the GLP-1 House by @weightwatchersclinic was incredible. As a longtime WeightWatchers member, I cannot tell you how excited I was to discover that they’ve launched WeightWatchers Clinic. It connects you with a specialized clinician to determine your eligibility for clinical interventions. Even more - they have a new GLP-1 Program that offers specific behavioral support for those taking GLP-1 medications.

I met other GLP-1 girlies who were so inspirational. We bonded over lifelong weight struggles and food noise and were empowered by @drnadolsky to shed any shame on using these drugs because they are a treatment, not a shortcut! GLP-1s have helped me so much and will help so many other people live their lives again. For the first time in forever, I feel in control. I used to get so much anxiety about food and my body that I would panic before social events. Dinners. Parties. Vacations. Sporting events. The voice in my head was debilitating. 

I’m so grateful for @weightwatchersclinic and can’t wait to help spread the education that will undoubtedly change people’s lives. What a time to be alive! 

Click the link in my bio to join WW’s program and use my special promo code Taylor10 for $10 off your membership! *With select plan purchase. Restr. apply. Offer ends 3/31/24.
